{"tid":2390410,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己嘅人生係錯撚晒","createTime":"2021-02-01T13:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T20:23:34.000Z","uid":126626,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9c072e04d0adec75f2dd3e889dea9428097e6195","tid":2390410,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"細細個讀書唔好，因為照顧自己嘅姨媽叫自己俾心機讀書，所以好辛苦考到入Kong U。<br />\n<br />\nyr 1掛住拍拖，散咗之後再拍拖，又掛住搵錢同女朋友去食好嘢去旅行，畢業之後叫做搵到本科工作，人工都唔錯，之後轉工，收入都幾好，仲買咗樓。<br />\n<br />\n但係又覺得自己唔鍾意呢行，同埋嗰陣都係為咗同當時嘅女朋友做同一行。於是辭咗職轉工，再進修，點知撞正肺炎，自己想轉嗰行又俾政府搞緊，結果長期冇收入，要賣車。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家笑我咁戇鳩買樓，到而家都未坐完SSD。<br />\n<br />\n見到做以前嗰行嘅朋友全部都撈得好店，呢排疫情，其實一樣多人要Audit。<br />\n<br />\n結果明明條路都好大路，最後都比自己玩爛晒，覺得自己係一個垃圾&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9c1242f8126aab7de27cf4765442ae005eed6134","tid":2390410,"uid":356010,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"行錯一次，唔好直接否定自己的人生"},{"pid":"a8f9d62e9edc117fa19cf63b26411a74a99f0fc2","tid":2390410,"uid":126626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"同父母關係唔好，不嬲都係姨媽湊大我，呢排佢糖尿病好嚴重，結果自己都要買返車去車佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢知道我要賣車已經問我係咪好唔掂，喺佢面前真係打唔到成熟，喊得好緊要。<br />\n<br />\n諗住過多年就放咗層樓，攞返少少錢，睇吓會唔會放棄進修，做返以前嗰行。<br />\n<br />\n好似浪費咗好多時間&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e5c1bf3fa9287ff9a455a8bc0b78bcbc5a9a9013","tid":2390410,"uid":71508,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"你嘅人生咁好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅"},{"pid":"7dbfa2f6b06f22f12a2ff9d14996f8ddea45f830","tid":2390410,"uid":13118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"唔錯呀, 至少你好過"},{"pid":"d585b269ebdebbf9736066f77bfe707c098a6ae7","tid":2390410,"uid":126626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"炒股票又唔識，買樓又買錯區，花咗幾年時間同前度糾纏， 30歲人都成個垃圾咁<br />\n<br />\n讀大學嘅時候成日都諗，自己會唔會有啲咩好嘅前途，望住啲大仙畢業，依家好多都名成利就，自己唔知做緊乜&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ee09ee406915aa3cb7e1e9ebfe75b1ca2c8a40ec","tid":2390410,"uid":2734,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"屌你又車又樓又女 錯咩鳩"},{"pid":"53b8f90166b39754293c56777d04b0aa3d2118a1","tid":2390410,"uid":208323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"樓主人生勝利組"},{"pid":"5bf3988c22dfbf5aa3e2f14fecc6d33b1a351185","tid":2390410,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"有樓又有女又有錢　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19f6a35cdf5ed10859f922f0e2b421f4e06c3eb","tid":2390410,"uid":27609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"你已經好好....hku做乜西都得啦<br />\n仲有樓"},{"pid":"9f79ef412e96bf7cc056468696108f22a4bc2acb","tid":2390410,"uid":16061,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"點樣錯撚晒<br />\n咁多手足著草坐監<br />\n個啲就真係錯撚晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d7685cb213d02b0329a8b11d2ef1ca7524c4a1","tid":2390410,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"那有樓，那有車，那有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15794749c27f817330d0697b353e6e1a626fed78","tid":2390410,"uid":298150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"冇話咩叫錯咩叫岩。只係你自己鍾意同人比較。<br />\n路係自己決定，做左就唔會望番轉頭。自己做既決定當時覺得岩就過得自己。人比人比死人。自己心理質素唔夠多番去睇下書或者做多少少準備。"},{"pid":"0f823fc2968ba1e01db3cd8d11e0a439499a7001","tid":2390410,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"呢一年冇咩收入其實都用晒啲積蓄，因為要供樓，同埋姨媽身體唔好，用咗好多錢照顧佢。<br />\n<br />\n自己住嘅地方，係之前買落，而家樓價一定唔好，當時係諗住同當時嘅女朋友結婚。<br />\n<br />\n應該都會放咗層樓，玩返少少錢，睇吓可唔可以租一個地方同姨媽一齊住。<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，都係想呻下自己行錯路，應該都會放棄教書，返返去做本行。多謝大家鼓勵，唔好意思"},{"pid":"c1887116b7b462309cb5b6d6a2b88689e1bd7abf","tid":2390410,"uid":108275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會諗過不斷做錯決定既人一定有原因？利申我人生都係錯撚晒"},{"pid":"22de577f57c17ab5d269586441f79dbf8e4374fe","tid":2390410,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"做唔到誠哥個仔我真係錯撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905b46bbd81b2589a3279151e9eaf836a14c027f","tid":2390410,"uid":31080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"每當決擇時都選擇左自己當刻最想做嘅事<br />\n咁你無得後悔 至少你無後顧咁開心過痛快過<br />\n<br />\n如果每個選擇都要揀最大利益化果項 <br />\n做人點得開心<br />\n窮咪窮 最多咪唔生仔 <br />\n人好短命架咋 錢帶唔到落去"},{"pid":"e52ef28bb4cf48bc5fdcf8a302e286739902b05c","tid":2390410,"uid":113929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"完，哂命 post"},{"pid":"840b3ed154c6e1f9d828a5c571850af4b5d222a8","tid":2390410,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"有Mandy你玩晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a290b4ce9043696bb06d3af6f8c49a53e72f24a","tid":2390410,"uid":933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"起樓主底發現之前有睇開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲嘢可能命水生成 唔好太怪責自己 始終我地都生活係一個扭曲嘅社會"},{"pid":"b6f3d0fe371d7e286ae7c4d36a9d5028cfa4f020","tid":2390410,"uid":136061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d585b269ebdebbf9736066f77bfe707c098a6ae7","tid":2390410,"uid":126626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"炒股票又唔識，買樓又買錯區，花咗幾年時間同前度糾纏， 30歲人都成個垃圾咁<br />\n<br />\n讀大學嘅時候成日都諗，自己會唔會有啲咩好嘅前途，望住啲大仙畢業，依家好多都名成利就，自己唔知做緊乜&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"買左邊區"},{"pid":"ae147aa88c61baa87c2d748de5744e7025f9fabb","tid":2390410,"uid":326957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結果明明條路都好大路，最後都比自己玩爛晒，覺得自己係一個垃圾&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你開post係想曬命嘅  <br />\n而家曬完啦 滿意未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你真心覺得自己失敗嘅 <br />\n咁冇車冇樓冇女嘅毒撚點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有咁嘅心態 無論你有再好嘅環境 你都唔會覺得開心<br />\n靠比較得到嘅快樂係唔會長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198d51ae9139317265ed0d9435d022cb4cc25151","tid":2390410,"uid":297738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"睇返樓主你啲post，覺得你仲好留戀以前。有時世界好公平，太早過啲光輝嘅日子，往後嘅生活就會好唔慣，好想再過多一次。<br />\n<br />\n一日你認定過去係你人生最好嘅日子，一日你都唔會好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"51ca4d568529bd349fccbbbade0fe60fca456445","tid":2390410,"uid":284018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"人比人永遠都比唔上<br />\n老土啲講句珍惜多啲身邊嘅人<br />\n多啲陪下你姨媽<br />\n不過你簡左呢條路 都獲得你想要嘅野<br />\n只係你未滿足"},{"pid":"36ad72dd5c31b5f31ade8d6a2fc166902addc3c9","tid":2390410,"uid":17281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"驚咩 <br />\n我Ugrad之後都廢足8年<br />\n見到個個同學考哂牌係有d灰<br />\n但人生仲有幾十年做 怕咩遲"}]}